summary: anyways was rewatching snufkin and the park keeper and idk if this was obvious and im stupid or what but it just hit me that at...
body: anyways was rewatching snufkin and the park keeper and idk if this was obvious and im stupid or what but it just hit me that at the end, when moomin was giving snufkin his “punishment” of making 5000 signs, snufkin thought moomin was giving him a legitimate punishment for abandoning him at the party. hence the flashback and the “i suppose it’s all i deserve”. this boy thought- and ACCEPTED- that his best friend was punishing him for leaving. he looked legitimately surprised when moomin made his “let’s get snufkin out of jail” plan actually apparent.
